Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Wealth Management
Addenda Capital Inc. operates as an investment advisory firm. The Company provides investment management services to high-net-worth individuals, as well as offers investment solutions. Addenda Capital serves customers in Canada.




