Company Overview of Addenda Capital Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Addenda Capital Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides wealth management services to its clients. It provides services to high net worth clients, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations or other businesses, insurance companies, foundations, endowments funds, third party mutual funds of major financial institutions, and labour-sponsored funds. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity markets across the North America region and in fixed i...
Addenda Capital Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm also provides wealth management services to its clients. It provides services to high net worth clients, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations or other businesses, insurance companies, foundations, endowments funds, third party mutual funds of major financial institutions, and labour-sponsored funds. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity markets across the North America region and in fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in alternative investments markets. The firm primarily invests in value and growth stocks employing fundamental and quantitative analysis, with a focus on top-down analysis to create its portfolios. For fixed income, it invests in long term bonds, corporate bonds, short term bonds, multi-strategy bonds, government bonds, global bonds, high yield bonds, commercial mortgages, North American preferred shares, and global sovereign, global credit, and emerging markets securities. Addenda Capital Inc. was founded in 1996 and is based in Montreal, Canada with additional offices in Toronto, Canada, Guelph, Canada, and Regina, Canada.
